@startuml architecturalknowledgedb-main-activity
title ArchitecturalKnowledgeDB - Main Activity

start
:Configure AKDB_DATABASE_PATH and optional source root;
:Register or select project;

if (Source corpus imported?) then (no)
  :Import ADRs, documents, rules, definitions, UML;
  :Update SQLite knowledge items and FTS;
else (yes)
endif

if (Repository provenance needed?) then (yes)
  :Register repository path;
  :Scan Git metadata read-only;
  :Store selected commits and changed files;
endif

:Run search, context pack, consistency, or staleness command;

if (Optional vector backend configured?) then (yes)
  :Embed changed items or run hybrid recall;
else (no)
  :Use FTS recall baseline;
endif

if (MCP bulk/list/search call?) then (yes)
  :Return compact response by default;
  if (detail=full requested?) then (yes)
    :Include complete source/prose fields;
  else (no)
  endif
else (no)
endif

:Return source-anchored context, recall neighborhood, or findings;

if (Sources changed?) then (yes)
  :Reingest from owning folders;
else (no)
endif

if (Public website projection changed?) then (yes)
  :Update product-facts and curated website deep dive;
  :Refresh deploy snapshot and Atlas/product tests;
else (no)
endif

stop

@enduml
